---
description: Keep content changes translated and cross-page consistent
alwaysApply: true
---

# Content Change Guardrails

- When editing or adding user-facing copy, update translation entries in `frontend/src/i18n/messages.js` in the same change.
- If a key is missing in a non-English locale, add it before finishing; do not leave newly introduced English-only UI labels.
- Keep language labels/code options in sync with supported locales.

# Cross-Page Impact Checks

- Treat page edits as site-level changes: verify related pages, nav labels, dropdown items, and footer links for consistency.
- If one page changes positioning/terminology, update matching references on other pages.
- Before finalizing, run frontend validation (`npm run lint` and `npm run build`) and fix any issues introduced by the change.
